  "theorem": {
    "latex_statement": "\\begin{theorem}[B2 endpoint boundary, paper-local finite form]\\label{thm:b2-endpoint-boundary}\nInside the certified endpoint-24 quotient by the verified free $T/K$ action, the B2 boundary is selected by affine selected values together with non-affine cell-value labelling.  Equivalently, the exact finite selector is \\texttt{selected\\_value\\_affine\\_and\\_cell\\_value\\_nonaffine}.  It selects 8 quotient orbits and 32 records, and these orbits match the eight P3 canonicalized selected-affine boundary components, each of size four.\n\\end{theorem}",
